{"tid":702900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑片] 荃灣私家車越線加速衝路障 阿Sir竟踢雪糕筒企圖攔截該車","createTime":"2018-06-15T09:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T12:14:50.000Z","uid":2547,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9709bb6b36eacb1cf052a1516e02fb263d780a8b","tid":702900,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YWsO85naBmw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYWsO85naBmw&d=YnwWlSBWHhr3D8QJ6eb0lEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=fe4071d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YWsO85naBmw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/174206_58cc4da0b394c3cac39cbecb86f651f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F174206_58cc4da0b394c3cac39cbecb86f651f9.jpg&h=76fbacf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通警急踢雪樣筒攔截無果<br />\n<br />\n當時，左邊一名交通警舉手示意後方另一輛黑色私家車停車，但對方未有理會，加速駛往第四線逃走，只見一名交通警狂奔往第四線，並踢跌一個雪糕筒嘗試制止無果。黑色私家車輾過雪糕筒後，加速逃去。事後一輛警車立即開車追截，而警員一度狼狽檢拾雪糕筒。<br />\n<br />\n警方展開追截　私家車向屯門方向逃去無蹤<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf7bc66b38abda588539569732a4a96e1405bec","tid":702900,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bb7769e4527a8a76a7b74ad9162dc7becee82c","tid":702900,"uid":33433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"拿 香港差佬呢就"},{"pid":"25cd402df72b8cce5a06b375159c664765cd1551","tid":702900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockq